17:35.542 --> 17:44.454
It's only last couple hours, but I mean, it's party time, but I'm telling you, in life, we know what it's like to be in darkness.

17:45.095 --> 17:53.666
But every single day, no matter how dark Jesus is alive, He has risen, the sun is shining, and He's got a brand new beginning for you.

17:53.706 --> 17:56.370
Embrace it, grab onto it.

17:56.514 --> 17:57.115
believe it.

17:57.435 --> 18:03.425
And finally, if Jesus really rose, that means Jesus is who He said He was.

18:04.787 --> 18:05.969
