18:06.850 --> 18:09.655
John 14, 6, Jesus answered, you want to know who I am?

18:10.196 --> 18:12.580
I am the way, the truth, and the life.

18:13.020 --> 18:15.384
And no one comes to the Father except through me.

18:15.885 --> 18:20.452
If just some person shows up and tells you that, you should look at them and laugh.

18:22.856 --> 18:24.178
But when they're dead

18:24.898 --> 18:28.283
and nailed to a cross and buried.

18:28.343 --> 18:31.568
And then they walk out.

18:32.329 --> 18:35.093
You might go, I'm following you.

18:35.133 --> 18:37.937
He's the way, the truth, and the life.

18:37.957 --> 18:39.119
You want to get to the Father.

18:39.179 --> 18:40.481
You want to find God.

18:40.501 --> 18:41.903
You want to know God's love.

18:41.923 --> 18:43.205
You want to know God's promise.

18:43.225 --> 18:44.026
There's one way.

18:44.587 --> 18:49.394
Follow the risen Savior, Jesus Christ, and He will take you all the way there.

